  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p>This application does not collect personal data directly.</p>

  <p>We may interact with third-party services (e.g., Telegram, TON Wallets) which provide limited public data such as wallet addresses or Telegram usernames for app functionality.</p>

  <ul>
    <li>No passwords, private keys, or sensitive user data are collected or stored.</li>
    <li>Blockchain data may be publicly accessible on-chain.</li>
    <li>We may use analytics tools that collect anonymized data to improve user experience.</li>
  </ul>

  <p>By using this app, you consent to this privacy policy. Changes may be made without prior notice.</p>

